LICENSE
=======

Applied Energistics: Crystal Science


Licensing Overview
------------------

Applied Energistics: Crystal Science uses a multi-license structure.
Different parts of the project are licensed under different licenses.

This file describes which licenses apply to which parts of the project,
as well as the corresponding authorship information.
Full, unmodified license texts are provided with this project.


